init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It's a bit of a shock to the Dads who now find out that they are at the bottom of the barrel.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: One Dad, however, is determined to make it better for all the Dads.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The other Dads cheer, get up, and begin to leave the meeting.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The next week, they all go to the support group.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The first Dad says he went home and changed the number on the mug.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They talked about how much more praise and attention they had gotten from their families.
